[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":222},["Reactive",2],{"content-/blog/my-first-project-with-kirby":3,"content-query-CvR2m5YUVX":138},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":7,"title":8,"description":9,"author":10,"dates":11,"image":13,"body":14,"_type":133,"_id":134,"_source":135,"_file":136,"_extension":137},"/blog/my-first-project-with-kirby","blog",false,"","My First Project with Kirby","this is a small description about me for my blog alsdfaldfs alsdfkasfd","@bruno",{"published":12},"2024-04-030","/inclousion.webp",{"type":15,"children":16,"toc":124},"root",[17,26,43,50,55,61,68,73,79,84,119],{"type":18,"tag":19,"props":20,"children":22},"element","h1",{"id":21},"launching-my-first-project-with-kirby-cms-a-unique-rapid-development-experience",[23],{"type":24,"value":25},"text","Launching My First Project with Kirby CMS: A Unique, Rapid Development Experience",{"type":18,"tag":27,"props":28,"children":29},"p",{},[30,32,41],{"type":24,"value":31},"I'm excited to share my latest project, ",{"type":18,"tag":33,"props":34,"children":38},"a",{"href":35,"rel":36},"https://www.inclousion.ch/",[37],"nofollow",[39],{"type":24,"value":40},"Inclousion.ch",{"type":24,"value":42},", where I ventured into new territories with Kirby CMS, enhanced by the utility-first approach of Tailwind CSS and the simplicity of Alpine.js.",{"type":18,"tag":44,"props":45,"children":47},"h2",{"id":46},"introduction-to-the-project",[48],{"type":24,"value":49},"Introduction to the Project",{"type":18,"tag":27,"props":51,"children":52},{},[53],{"type":24,"value":54},"This project marked my first experience with Kirby CMS. Kirby offers a flexible, file-based CMS that eliminates the need for a database, which intrigued me from the start. I decided to pair it with Tailwind CSS for styling and Alpine.js for the minimal interactive components, aiming for a lean and efficient tech stack.",{"type":18,"tag":44,"props":56,"children":58},{"id":57},"development-experience",[59],{"type":24,"value":60},"Development Experience",{"type":18,"tag":62,"props":63,"children":65},"h3",{"id":64},"kirby-cms",[66],{"type":24,"value":67},"Kirby CMS",{"type":18,"tag":27,"props":69,"children":70},{},[71],{"type":24,"value":72},"Kirby's learning curve was steep yet rewarding. Its no-database, file-driven approach made it exceptionally straightforward to setup and deploy. The CMS's panel is intuitive, allowing me to manage content flexibly without relying on traditional database constraints.",{"type":18,"tag":44,"props":74,"children":76},{"id":75},"lessons-learned-and-conclusion",[77],{"type":24,"value":78},"Lessons Learned and Conclusion",{"type":18,"tag":27,"props":80,"children":81},{},[82],{"type":24,"value":83},"This project was an excellent first foray into using Kirby CMS. It provided a fast development cycle, thanks to the combined power of Kirby, Tailwind CSS, and Alpine.js. Each tool offered its unique strengths:",{"type":18,"tag":85,"props":86,"children":87},"ul",{},[88,99,109],{"type":18,"tag":89,"props":90,"children":91},"li",{},[92,97],{"type":18,"tag":93,"props":94,"children":95},"strong",{},[96],{"type":24,"value":67},{"type":24,"value":98}," for its simplicity and flexibility in content management.",{"type":18,"tag":89,"props":100,"children":101},{},[102,107],{"type":18,"tag":93,"props":103,"children":104},{},[105],{"type":24,"value":106},"Tailwind CSS",{"type":24,"value":108}," for its speed and utility-first design philosophy.",{"type":18,"tag":89,"props":110,"children":111},{},[112,117],{"type":18,"tag":93,"props":113,"children":114},{},[115],{"type":24,"value":116},"Alpine.js",{"type":24,"value":118}," for its minimalist approach to adding interactivity.",{"type":18,"tag":27,"props":120,"children":121},{},[122],{"type":24,"value":123},"Overall, this project not only enhanced my skills but also added a unique piece to my portfolio. For fellow developers considering this tech stack, I highly recommend diving in; it's well worth the learning curve!",{"title":7,"s